\caption{ First order mass flux term $\tilde{j}_1$. Small (a) and large (b) $\tilde x$ behavior for $\mathcal {R}=0$ and 30. 
Open circles in (a) correspond to the purely kinetic regime, equation (\ref{Solution_flux_only_R}) with $\mathcal {R}=30$.
